-- Heartbeat: a periodic check-in turn on the MAIN session (full conversation
-- context, unlike cron's fresh subagents). Each idle tick hands the agent the
-- checklist; it replies HEARTBEAT_OK when nothing needs attention and the bot
-- stays silent — you only hear about real alerts. Busy or out-of-window ticks
-- are skipped (timing is approximate; use cron for exact-time jobs). Test a
-- checklist with: shell3 dev --heartbeat
